body: No comment for this masterpiece. Sad, really sad, nhentai you're disappointing me. Yes, this is one of the authors hardest and most rapey doujin still a masterful work. Every of his story feels as written by Sigsawa himself, I'm amazed. This is why doujinshi have a right for existence, as they can be the erotic expansion for a story. -The world is not beautiful therefore it is-
